ğŸ“Œ Overview

This interactive Tableau dashboard analyzes customer churn patterns to help organizations identify at-risk customers, understand churn drivers, and design targeted retention strategies.
The dashboard provides visibility into churn KPIs, customer segmentation, and cohort trends, enabling business teams to make data-driven retention decisions.

