ğŸ¯ Business Problem

Customer churn is one of the most expensive problems for subscription-based businesses.
Most companies struggle to answer:

Who is leaving?

Why are they leaving?

When are they most likely to churn?

Which customer segments are at highest risk?

This dashboard solves these questions using exploratory analytics, KPIs, and segmentation.

